S & P affirms Swire " A " , rates perpetual bond A - minus . Standard and Poor ' s rating agnecy on Wednesday said it affirmed its " A " long - term corporate credit rating on Swire Pacific Ltd . The agency also said it assigned an A - minus rating to the US $ 300 million Cumulative Guaranteed Pertetual Capital Securities issued by Swire Pacific Offshore Financing Ltd and guaranteed on a subordinated basis by Swire Pacific Ltd . Standard and Poor ' s said the lower rating reflected the subordination and interest deferral option of the Securities . 
